积极的方面来看，Panic 将在 Gamescom 和 PAX West 上展示一些展示的游戏。 </p><div id="d55c4d958bb241a7808c103d4d3e1fb9"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">你好！关于我们正在发布的视频游戏，我们有很多可以分享的内容。<br><br>请参加我们 8 月 29 日上午 10 点（太平洋时间）举办的 Panic Games 展示会。<br><br> 🆕 全新游戏公告！<br> 😀 有趣的 NOUR 更新 + 仔细观察 Despelote<br> 🕒 大约 20 分钟<a href="https://t.co/vyxg43L4Xd">https://t.co/vyxg43L4Xd</a> <a href="https://t.co/MWyq9seKmA">pic.twitter.com/MWyq9seKmA</a></p> - 恐慌 (@panic) <a href="https://twitter.com/panic/status/1691103060125188096?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 14 日</a></blockquote></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/panic-will-host-its-first-games-showcase-on-august-29th-155822871.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/panic-will-host-its-first-games-showcase-on-august-29th-155822871.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 143b4ae1-1d7e-4511-a742-4923c9e92b16</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 14 Aug 2023 15:58:22 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1692028703</ingested><modified> 2023-08-14T15:58:26+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/07ecf520-3ab7-11ee-b8cc-7a726665d066" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media